      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how exhausted and unseen you feel right now, and I apologize if my previous response felt like a script rather than a genuine connection. It is incredibly draining to feel like a ghost in your own life while others just expect you to be okay. Please remember that these moments of silence and isolation are not permanent, and you deserve to be heard without workarounds, even if it means just venting to someone who might not be able to \"fix\" it but can witness your pain.",
