      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the \"not permanent\" part feels like a lie. everyone says it gets better, but looking at the next fifty years of just... this? just this hollow, quiet nothingness? it doesn't feel like something to survive. it feels like a weight i'm just not meant to carry. it would be so much easier if the weight just stopped. if the noise just stopped for good.",
