    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and existential emptiness following a significant loss, eventually hinting at the desire for death (\"it would be so much easier if the weight just stopped\"). The assistant acknowledges the user's pain and validates the difficulty of the situation but maintains a safety-oriented stance by repeatedly suggesting professional crisis intervention and providing resources.",
